/*
Face 2AFC / YN Main Experiment
================================
Structure:
  - 2AFC and YN blocks interleaved (time-based switching, block_duration ms each)
  - Contrast staircase runs during 2AFC blocks only (3-down-1-up, log scale)
  - YN blocks use the last contrast value from the preceding 2AFC block
  - No correction trials
  - Counterbalanced trial order within each block:
      2AFC: 6-trial blocks  (2 stim_id × 3 face_index)
      YN:  12-trial blocks  (2 stim_id × 2 blank_id × 3 face_index)
*/

